Source:        Microsoft-Windows-StorageManagement-WSP-Spaces
Event ID:      2005
Task Category: None
Level:         Error
Description:
An error occurred during storage job execution.

Job Name:	Repair
Error Code:	4
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

